10/05/2004
BUCHAREST, Romania -- In all, 24 candidates will run for mayor of Bucharest during the 6 June local elections, according to the Municipal Electoral Bureau.
The deadline for submitting the necessary paperwork expired Saturday (8 May), as it did for those seeking to enter county and municipal councillor elections.
(Rompres - 10/05/04;
Mediafax - 09/05/04)
